title: KING JOFFREY SURROUNDED: Game of Thrones - Seven Kingdoms Total War Mod Gameplay
description:
KING JOFFREY SURROUNDED: Game of Thrones - Seven Kingdoms Total War Mod Gameplay - Hey guys!  Welcome Back to another Game of Thrones Battle.  This time King Joffrey is being ambushed and he has to rely on the Hound and his King's Guard.  Jackie will be joining me once again playing as House Dyane.  And I fight as the Crownlands.  Enjoy the Ambush Battle :D
